Exandria Unlimited Overview

Exandria Unlimited (EXU) is a series of mini-campaigns set within the world of Exandria, maintaining canonical continuity while showcasing different Dungeon Masters and players alongside original Critical Role cast members.

Art By: @CriticalRole

Series Breakdown

Exandria Unlimited Prime: The inaugural series follows the Crown Keepers, adventurers from TalDorei, in the year 842 PD. Set nearly three decades after the Chroma Conclaves assault and six years post-Campaign Two, the Crown Keepers unite to secure the Circlet of Barbed Vision, safeguarding its dangerous powers from malevolent forces.

Exandria Unlimited: Kymal: A two-part installment where the Crown Keepers embark on a daring casino heist in Kymal.

Exandria Unlimited: Calamity: Introduces new characters set during the Age of Arcanum, nearly a thousand years prior to current events.

Exandria Unlimited: Burden of the Crown: Follows the aftermath of the Kymal heist, focusing on Opals transformation into the Twice Crowned Champion of the Spider Queen amidst escalating conflicts.
